{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HIDDevice.sendReport()","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice/sendReport","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebHID_API\">WebHID API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice\"><code>HIDDevice</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice/collections\"><code>collections</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice/inputreport_event\"><code>HIDDevice: inputreport event</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice/opened\"><code>opened</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice/productId\"><code>productId</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice/productName\"><code>productName</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice/vendorId\"><code>vendorId</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice/open\"><code>open()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice/receiveFeatureReport\"><code>receiveFeatureReport()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice/sendFeatureReport\"><code>sendFeatureReport()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>sendReport()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for WebHID API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HID\"><code>HID</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDConnectionEvent\"><code>HIDConnectionEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDInputReportEvent\"><code>HIDInputReportEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/hid\"><code>Navigator.hid</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard secure\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Secure context:</strong> This feature is available only in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\">secure contexts</a> (HTTPS), in some or all <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">supporting browsers</a>.</p></div><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>This is an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Writing_guidelines/Experimental_deprecated_obsolete#experimental\">experimental technology</a></strong><br>Check the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility table</a> carefully before using this in production.</p></div>\n<p>The <strong><code>sendReport()</code></strong> method of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice\"><code>HIDDevice</code></a> interface sends an output report to the HID device.</p>\n<p>The <code>reportId</code> for each of the report formats that this device supports can be retrieved from <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice/collections\"><code>HIDDevice.collections</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js-nolint notranslate\">sendReport(reportId, data)\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"reportid\"><code>reportId</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>An 8-bit report ID. If the HID device does not use report IDs, send <code>0</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"data\"><code>data</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Bytes as an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/ArrayBuffer\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a>, a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypedArray\"><code>TypedArray</code></a>, or a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/DataView\"><code>DataView</code></a>.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"return_value","title":"Return value","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> that resolves with <code>undefined</code> once the report has been sent.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exceptions","title":"Exceptions","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"notallowederror\"><code>NotAllowedError</code> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Thrown if sending the report fails for any reason.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>The example below shows how to make a Joy-Con device rumble using output reports. You can see more examples, and live demos in the article <a href=\"https://web.dev/hid/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Connecting to uncommon HID devices</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// First, send a command to enable vibration.</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Magical bytes come from https://github.com/mzyy94/joycon-toolweb</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> enableVibrationData <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x48</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x01</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> device<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sendReport</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0x01</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Uint8Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>enableVibrationData<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Then, send a command to make the Joy-Con device rumble.</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Actual bytes are available in the sample below.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> rumbleData <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* â€¦ */</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> device<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sendReport</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0x10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Uint8Array</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>rumbleData<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://wicg.github.io/webhid/#dom-hiddevice-sendreport","title":"WebHID API"}],"query":"api.HIDDevice.sendReport"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.HIDDevice.sendReport","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice/sendReport/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The sendReport() method of the HIDDevice interface sends an output report to the HID device.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-09-13T05:48:35.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/hiddevice/sendreport","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/hiddevice/sendreport/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/8573240024adc1eef906b4b2df35567144fd733e","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice","title":"HIDDevice"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HIDDevice/sendReport","title":"HIDDevice.sendReport()"}],"pageTitle":"HIDDevice.sendReport() - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}